@startuml clustering_comparison
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #1a1a2e
skinparam defaultFontColor #eaeaea

title Clustering Algorithm Comparison

|k-Means|
:Specify k clusters;
:Initialise centroids;
:Assign points to nearest;
:Update centroids;
:Repeat until convergence;
note right: Fast, assumes\nspherical clusters

|Hierarchical|
:Compute distance matrix;
:Merge closest clusters;
:Build dendrogram;
:Cut at desired level;
note right: No k needed,\nvisualise structure

|DBSCAN|
:Set eps and min_samples;
:Find core points;
:Expand clusters;
:Mark noise points;
note right: Finds arbitrary\nshapes, handles noise

@enduml
